'''Research assistants''' were the lowest ranking personnel of the [[New Republic Diplomatic Corps/Legends|New Republic Diplomatic Corps]]. Their duty was to gather information and data files for [[Ambassador/Legends|ambassadors]], [[Diplomat/Legends|diplomats]], [[New Republic Observer|Observers]], and protocol [[Officer/Legends|officers]].

